Russia ’s central bank plans to seek
the authority to examine the way in which the nation’s banks set
bonus compensation for top managers as part of a bid to assess
their financial health,  Kommersant  said, citing documentation
from Bank Rossii.  To contact the reporter on this story: Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow
